| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6861 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: be3c2f0a-f0bf-581c-8821-a7f2abd413cb"
